{
  "stem": "2830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only place was where you were born, and that-- our family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in 1942, they began to be that they gonna liquidate all the Jews, all the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're gonna make clean from Jews, of course, judenrein.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I happened to be in the-- with the-- listening in where they-- they had a conference in the judenrein.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I listened in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said, well, the girls have a chance to go to Germany on Aryan papers, you know, to hide as Aryans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for the boys, I'm afraid there is no chance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a dead giveaway that they're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The partisans did not care for the Jews being part of them, I remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't want to accept them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of them that I adored-- his name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was, you know-- I-- I really was so attached to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went, and he was killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the partisans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one went to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he escaped from Majdanek last time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was told by my sister, because she kept in touch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was much older than I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he escaped, and he was killed too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Cause the fight.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all three were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whoever went, you know, into the forest to the partisans--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And to the end, we went-- there is no place where to hide.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, you know, by Friday, they said they're gonna have to-- everybody's got to leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not one Jew is gonna remain in the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the only-- my-- my parents--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they had a bunker--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with a-- with, you know, friends of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They figured the war was gonna only last maybe two more weeks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they're gonna survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
